entry.tran: 过度疲惫的；累得阴郁（或烦躁）的
entry.def: If you are overtired, you are so tired that you feel unhappy or bad-tempered, or feel that you cannot do things properly.

example.ex: Make sure you avoid getting overtired or missing meals, when at all possible.
example.tran: 尽可能避免过度劳累或不按时吃饭。
